ZH: 我们要去山上爬山。
EN: We are going to climb the mountain.

ZH: 我在山上看到了一只小熊。
EN: I saw a small bear on the mountain.

ZH: 山的风景非常漂亮。
EN: The scenery of the mountain is very beautiful.

ZH: 春天，山上开满了鲜花。
EN: In spring, the mountain is covered with blooming flowers.

ZH: 我家附近有座很高的山。
EN: There is a very tall mountain near my house.

ZH: 山的顶上布满了厚厚的积雪。
EN: The top of the mountain is covered with thick snow.

ZH: 我喜欢在山中漫步。
EN: I enjoy taking a leisurely walk in the mountains.

ZH: 没有任何人在这座山上居住。
EN: Nobody lives on this mountain.

ZH: 在山上可以享受到清新的空气。
EN: You can enjoy the fresh air on the mountain.

ZH: 山中有很多野生动物。
EN: There are many wild animals in the mountains.

ZH: 我们要挑战那座高山。
EN: We are going to challenge that high mountain.

ZH: 山脚下有一个小溪。
EN: There is a stream at the foot of the mountain.

ZH: 爬山是一项很好的锻炼。
EN: Climbing mountains is a good exercise.

ZH: 山间的小路弯弯曲曲。
EN: The path in the mountains twists and turns.

ZH: 山区的气候非常寒冷。
EN: The climate in the mountainous region is very cold.

ZH: 山对我来说是一个伟大的难题。
EN: The mountain is a great challenge for me.

ZH: 山谷里回荡着鸟鸣。
EN: The valley echoes with bird songs.

ZH: 远处的山势雄峙。
EN: The distant mountain stands tall.

ZH: 我们在山上野餐。
EN: We are having a picnic on the mountain.

ZH: 山上温度很低，需要多穿几件衣服。
EN: The temperature on the mountain is low, so you need to wear more clothes.
